snippet: After a scoreless final four minutes, No. 20 Georgetown held off visiting Tennessee in a display of abysmal shooting in the SEC/Big East Challenge.
abstract: Georgetown beats Tennessee, 37-36, in men's college basketball; other college basketball results noted.
lead_paragraph: After a scoreless final four minutes, No. 20 Georgetown held off visiting Tennessee in a display of abysmal shooting in the SEC/Big East Challenge.

headline.seo: Georgetown Edges Tennessee in Display of Abysmal Shooting
